OL,3,COwner fined more than #2,000 over
OL,4,Cdangerous dogs
OL,6,FAn owner of three dangerous dogs has
OL,7,Fbeen fined more than #2,000.
OL,9,FKyle Muir, 30, of Thoresby Road in
OL,10,FYork, was given a warning after a
OL,11,Fseries of incidents involving the
OL,12,Fdogs, as well as anti-social
OL,13,Fbehaviour, York City Council said.
OL,15,FNeighbours had complained about the
OL,16,Fanimals repeatedly escaping and
OL,17,Fleaving them feeling unsafe.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
