FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1779789943
OL,3,COwner fined more than #2,000 over
OL,4,Cdangerous dogs
OL,6,FFrom November 2024, the pets entered
OL,7,Fneighbours' gardens, caused damage and
OL,8,Fbehaved in an uncontrolled and
OL,9,Faggressive way.
OL,11,FOn 30 September 2025, two of Muir's
OL,12,Fdogs forced entry into a neighbouring
OL,13,Fgarden and attacked another dog,
OL,14,Fcausing injuries that required
OL,15,Ftreatment by a vet.
OL,17,FBetween September 2025 and January of
OL,18,Fthis year, the dogs were reported to
OL,19,Fhave repeatedly escaped and strayed
OL,20,Finto neighbouring gardens, caused a
OL,21,Fnuisance and barked persistently.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1779789943
OL,3,COwner fined more than #2,000 over
OL,4,Cdangerous dogs
OL,6,FThe council and North Yorkshire Police
OL,7,Ffound one of the dogs, Fendi, was an
OL,8,Funregistered XL bully.
OL,10,FIn January, Muir asked officers to
OL,11,Ftake it from him, as he could no
OL,12,Flonger control it.
OL,14,FMuir was invited to a police interview
OL,15,Funder caution but he did not attend ot
OL,16,Frespond to followup enquiries.
OL,18,FAt York Magistrates' Court, he pleaded
OL,19,Fguilty to offences involving dangerous
OL,20,Fdogs and anti-social behaviour.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
