PN,36904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1779789943
OL,3,COwner fined more than #2,000 over
OL,4,Cdangerous dogs
OL,6,FHe was ordered to pay a total of
OL,7,F#2,762, including #500 compensation to
OL,8,Fthe owner of the dog that was attacked.
OL,10,FCllr Michael Pavlovic: "Failing to
OL,11,Ftrain and control dogs is not
OL,12,Facceptable and can be dangerous.
OL,14,F"Please report your concerns early, so
OL,15,Fwe can take robust enforcement action
OL,16,Fto protect our communities."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
